    public class StateImpl
extends ItemImpl
implements State
    An implementation of the model object ' State'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Package Class Name
    • Required Plugins
    • Revision
    • Timestamp
    • Deployable Unit Name
    • Job Family
    • Resource
    • Commit Ids
    • Commit Id
    • State Customizers
    • Project Name
